having one calf. 1) Taittirīya Saṃhitā, ii. 1, 5, 4; vi. 1, 3, 6; Kāṭhaka Saṃhitā, xxxvii. 5;
Taittirīya Brāhmaṇa, ii. 7, 4, 1, etc.

